# CodeCraft IDE Features

## Core Features
1. AI-Powered Code Analysis
   - Real-time code analysis for multiple languages
   - Error detection and suggestions
   - Code improvement recommendations
   - Support for Python, JavaScript, Java, C++, C, HTML, CSS, and TypeScript

2. Intelligent Code Fixing
   - One-click code fixes
   - Line-by-line error correction
   - Context-aware suggestions
   - Confidence scoring for fixes

3. Interactive Learning Environment
   - Clean, distraction-free interface
   - Single-file program execution
   - Instant feedback on code changes
   - Beginner-friendly design

4. AI Chat Assistant
   - 24/7 availability
   - Contextual help and hints
   - Personalized learning guidance
   - Real-time code explanations

5. Multi-language Support
   - Python
   - JavaScript
   - Java
   - C++
   - C
   - HTML
   - CSS
   - TypeScript

6. Code Translation
   - Language-to-language translation
   - Syntax conversion
   - Code adaptation

## Technical Features
1. Backend Services
   - RESTful API endpoints
   - Request validation
   - Error handling
   - Health monitoring
   - Service status checks

2. Frontend Features
   - Modern, responsive UI
   - Real-time code editing
   - Syntax highlighting
   - Code execution preview
   - Interactive tutorials

3. Security Features
   - Input validation
   - Error sanitization
   - Safe code execution environment
   - Rate limiting

4. Performance Features
   - Fast code analysis
   - Quick response times
   - Efficient error detection
   - Optimized code fixes

## User Experience
1. Learning Tools
   - Step-by-step guidance
   - Interactive challenges
   - Progress tracking
   - Community support

2. Interface Features
   - Clean, modern design
   - Intuitive navigation
   - Responsive layout
   - Dark/light mode support

3. Community Features
   - User collaboration
   - Progress sharing
   - Community support
   - Knowledge sharing
